title: Cisco Catalyst 9000: StackWise Virtual Link Interconnect Port State
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Monitors the StackWise Virtual Link (SVL) interconnect ports of a Cisco
 Catalyst 9000 series switch. The port and neighbor port operational state
 are read from the CISCO-STACKWISE-MIB (cswDistrStackPhyPortOperStatus).

 The check is OK when the port is up and CRITICAL when the port is down.

item:
 The physical stack port number.

inventory:
 One service is created per distributed stack physical port.
